Convert a Dataset(Connector) object to a CDISCDataset(Connector) object

as_cdisc.Rd

as_cdisc(
  x,
  parent = if (identical(get_dataname(x), "ADSL")) character(0) else "ADSL"
)

# S3 method for Dataset
as_cdisc(
  x,
  parent = if (identical(get_dataname(x), "ADSL")) character(0) else "ADSL"
)

# S3 method for DatasetConnector
as_cdisc(
  x,
  parent = if (identical(get_dataname(x), "ADSL")) character(0) else "ADSL"
)

Arguments

x

an object of Dataset or DatasetConnector class
parent

optional, (character)
parent dataset name

Value

(CDISCDataset or CDISCDatasetConnector) object

Details

Convert a Dataset(Connector) object to a CDISCDataset(Connector) object

Examples

# Dataset --------

library(random.cdisc.data)
as_cdisc(
  dataset(
    "ADSL",
    radsl(cached = TRUE),
    keys = get_cdisc_keys("ADSL"),
    code = "ADSL <- radsl(cached = TRUE)"
  )
)
#> <CDISCDataset>
#>   Inherits from: <Dataset>

# DatasetConnector --------

library(random.cdisc.data)
as_cdisc(
  rcd_dataset_connector(
    "ADSL",
    radsl,
    keys = get_cdisc_keys("ADSL")
  )
)
